Package Branch_And_Bound_TSP

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BnB_TSP
    Interface for all BnB_TSP variants, which implement different heuristics to speed up computation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BnB_TSP1
    Inheritor implementing trivial version of BnB_TSP heuristics, making it a near-exhaustive search.
    BnB_TSP2
    Inheritor implementing an improved bound function to improve computating speed.
    Branch_And_Bound_TSP_Test
    Branch_And_Bound_TSP Tester.
    SeqIter
    An iterator which scrolls through the unvisited interest points of a Request list.
    Template_BnB_TSP
    Template of a class that solves the Pickup/Delivery TSP problem using the Branch And Bound paradigm.
